## Rules

1. Return ONLY a JSON object. No prose before, no markdown fences, no commentary after.
2. Every required field in the schema must be present.
3. Prefer concrete values over placeholders. If the description lacks info for a field, make a reasonable inference, don't write "TODO" or "your-project-here".

